name: Air Defense!
description: The Kh-59MK2 missile and three kamikaze drones were negated
column4: which were going to destroy our energy infrastructure. "Shakhed" was shot down in the Dnipro and Kamian districts
column5: the missile - on the approach to the Dnipro.

name: Air Defense!
description: Six enemy "Shahed-136" drones were destroyed by the forces and means of anti-aircraft defense in the Mykolaiv region
column4: and one more by the soldiers of the National Guard of Ukraine.

name: Shahed Strike
column4: the Russians attacked Kyiv region with kamikaze drones. Our defenders managed to destroy 22 aerial targets.

name: the air alert lasted for more than four hours. The head of OVA reported
